data.value:
- Exit button: Ends the application.
- Check button: Check the eligibility of the student (yes/no).
- Register button:Add the student data to to the list, ready to be send to the Server.
- Update Button:Update student information from new entries from section one "Student Information".
- Delete Record: Delete the student’s Record selected in the list.
- Remove All button:All Students and Program information will be removed.
- Load Records to Server button: Upload all the records to the server.
